<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_880077_crossplan.CRSDB_Cat</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>CRSDB_Cat</name><script><![CDATA[var CRSDB_Cat = Class.create();
CRSDB_Cat.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    type: 'CRSDB_Cat'
};

CRSDB_Cat.create = function() {
    var cat = new GlideRecord('x_880077_crossplan_crsdb_category');
    cat.addQuery('type', 'provider');
    cat.addQuery('status', 'Waiting for Create');
    cat.query();
    while (cat.next()) {
        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_880077_crossplan_crs_jobqueue');
        gr.topic = "Create Category";
        var attributes = {
            "name": cat.name.toString(),
			"description" : cat.description.toString(),
			"parent" : cat.parent.toString(),
			"status" : cat.status.toString(),
			"type" : cat.type.toString()
        };
        gr.body = JSON.stringify(attributes);
        gr.state = "Ready";
// 		CRSLog.info(JSON.stringify(attributes));
        gr.insert();
    }
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-02-26 16:52:09</sys_created_on><sys_id>4790b730979121108ba1bde3f153af03</sys_id><sys_mod_count>23</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CRSDB_Cat</sys_name><sys_package display_value="CrossplaneV2" source="x_880077_crossplan">bdc0bd6847ba19104b6fcc88f36d43bd</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="CrossplaneV2">bdc0bd6847ba19104b6fcc88f36d43bd</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_4790b730979121108ba1bde3f153af03</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-02-26 22:19:25</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
